ments":[{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"--body","timestamp":1784340651395249001}],"created_at":1784338576027798001,"creation_channel":"cli","deps":[{"link_uuid":"78798936-b1ea-4ad4-acaa-08dc7ac474c6","relation":"discovered_from","target_id":"7c91-0488-6226-4a10"}],"description":"# Flaky: test_import_batch_resume._commit_count crashes on empty `git rev-list` output\n\n## Context (discovered during CI for bug 7c91-0488)\nOn gerrit-verify run 29620766631 (ubuntu py3.12 only; py3.11/py3.13/macos all passed), the\nintegration tier failed:\n\n    FAILED tests/interfaces/io/test_import_batch_resume.py::test_benchmark_commit_count_is_ceil_per_pass\n    E   ValueError: invalid literal for int() with base 10: ''   (test_import_batch_resume.py:51)\n\n## Root cause (suspected — not yet proven)\n`_commit_count` (tests/interfaces/io/test_import_batch_resume.py:45-51) runs\n`git rev-list --count HEAD` via subprocess.run WITHOUT check=True and WITHOUT guarding empty\nstdout, then `int(r.stdout.strip())`. In the concurrency/integration tier a timing race (tracker\nHEAD not yet present / transient git error) yields empty stdout -> int('') -> ValueError. Single-\ncell matrix failure = flake signature.\n\n## Suggested fix\nAssert the subprocess return code and non-empty stdout (or retry) before int(); fail with the\ngit stderr rather than an opaque int('') ValueError. Out of scope for the terraform-drift fix.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- _commit_count no longer raises int('') on empty/failed `git rev-list`; it either retries to a\n  ready HEAD or fails with a clear diagnostic including git's stderr.\n- The test passes deterministically across the py3.11/3.12/3.13 matrix.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"0562e26b-e567-442d-be46-f25fd0f76ede","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":3,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":["test","flaky","ci","import"],"ticket_id":"efb7-09de-8874-4658","ticket_type":"bug","title":"Flaky: test_import_batch_resume._commit_count int('') on empty git rev-list output","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["5814786a-ce85-4264-bc9b-b45acb8ce34b","78798936-b1ea-4ad4-acaa-08dc7ac474c6","0562e26b-e567-442d-be46-f25fd0f76ede","a111bad8-e115-44eb-8a55-08a40f927f63","f3169c0b-95ff-402a-b4ca-75425c437ec6","a5559856-992f-4ced-a599-f236d1cf9a2d"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784340897533170331,"uuid":"bb773263-9934-41ae-af88-9146912c23c2"}